other_tests.procedure_name: CT Abdomen and Pelvis with Contrast
other_tests.findings: Mild thickening of the left lateroconal fascia and mild fat stranding in the region of sigmoid diverticulosis; small hiatal hernia; mild intrahepatic and extrahepatic biliary dilatation; 8 mm hypodensity in the lower pole of the right kidney likely reflecting a simple renal cyst.
